820671,152,2455,2,29,1,105,15,"6.‘‘ Bhante nāgasena,‘ bhojanassa tīṇi aṅgāni gahetabbānī’ ti yaṃ vadesi, katamāni tāni tīṇi aṅgāni gahetabbānī’’ ti?"
820672,152,2455,30,50,1,134,13,"‘‘ Yathā, mahārāja, bhojanaṃ sabbasattānaṃ upatthambho, evameva kho, mahārāja, yoginā yogāvacarena sabbasattānaṃ maggupatthambhena bhavitabbaṃ. "
820673,152,2455,51,59,1,50,6,"Idaṃ, mahārāja, bhojanassa paṭhamaṃ aṅgaṃ gahetabbaṃ."
820674,152,2456,2,23,1,127,15,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, mahārāja, bhojanaṃ sabbasattānaṃ balaṃ vaḍḍheti, evameva kho, mahārāja, yoginā yogāvacarena puññavaḍḍhiyā vaḍḍhitabbaṃ. "
