820676,152,2457,2,23,1,134,14,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, mahārāja, bhojanaṃ sabbasattānaṃ abhipatthitaṃ, evameva kho, mahārāja, yoginā yogāvacarena sabbalokābhipatthitena bhavitabbaṃ. "
820677,152,2457,24,32,1,49,6,"Idaṃ, mahārāja, bhojanassa tatiyaṃ aṅgaṃ gahetabbaṃ. "
820678,152,2457,33,39,1,47,4,"Bhāsitampetaṃ, mahārāja, therena mahāmoggallānena–"
