822090,153,586,34,45,1,41,4,Pathavīdhātu[ paṭhavīdhātu( sī.)] āpodhātu tejodhātu vāyodhātu. 
822091,153,587,2,14,1,62,8,47. Dvīhi ākārehi dhātuyo pariggaṇhāti saṅkhepena ca vitthārena ca. 
822092,153,587,15,19,1,38,4,Kathaṃ vitthārena dhātuyo pariggaṇhāti? 
822093,153,587,20,44,1,205,20,"Vīsatiyā ākārehi pathavīdhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti, dvādasahi ākārehi āpodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti, catūhi ākārehi tejodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti, chahi ākārehi vāyodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti. "
822094,153,588,2,8,1,63,6,Katamehi vīsatiyā ākārehi pathavīdhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti? 
822095,153,588,9,50,1,245,30,"Atthi imasmiṃ kāye kesā lomā nakhā dantā taco, maṃsaṃ nhāru aṭṭhi aṭṭhimiñjaṃ[ aṭṭhimiñjā( sī.)] vakkaṃ, hadayaṃ yakanaṃ kilomakaṃ pihakaṃ papphāsaṃ, antaṃ antaguṇaṃ udariyaṃ karīsaṃ matthake matthaluṅganti imehi vīsatiyā ākārehi pathavīdhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti. "
822096,153,589,2,8,1,60,6,Katamehi dvādasahi ākārehi āpodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti? 
822097,153,589,9,30,1,157,21,Atthi imasmiṃ kāye pittaṃ semhaṃ pubbo lohitaṃ sedo medo assu vasā kheḷo siṅghāṇikā lasikā muttanti imehi dvādasahi ākārehi āpodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti. 
822098,153,590,2,9,1,58,6,Katamehi catūhi ākārehi tejodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti? 
822099,153,590,10,57,1,168,21,"Yena ca santappati, yena ca jīrīyati[ jīrati( sī.), jīrayati( ka.), passa ma. ni.3.351], yena ca pariḍayhati, yena ca asitapītakhāyitasāyitaṃ sammā pariṇāmaṃ gacchati, imehi catūhi ākārehi tejodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti. "
822100,153,591,2,8,1,57,6,Katamehi chahi ākārehi vāyodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti? 
822101,153,591,9,41,1,158,19,"Uddhaṅgamā vātā, adhogamā vātā, kucchisayā vātā, koṭṭhāsayā[ koṭṭhasayā( sī.)] vātā, aṅgamaṅgānusārino vātā, assāso passāso iti, imehi chahi ākārehi vāyodhātuṃ vitthārena pariggaṇhāti. "
822102,153,592,2,61,1,419,48,"Evaṃ imehi dvācattālīsāya ākārehi vitthārena dhātuyo sabhāvato upalakkhayanto tulayanto parivīmaṃsanto pariyogāhanto paccavekkhanto na kiñci gayhūpagaṃ passati kāyaṃ vā kāyapadesaṃ vā, yathā candanikaṃ pavicinanto na kiñci gayhūpagaṃ passeyya, yathā saṅkāraṭṭhānaṃ pavicinanto na kiñci gayhūpagaṃ passeyya, yathā vaccakuṭiṃ pavicinanto na kiñci gayhūpagaṃ passeyya, yathā sivathikaṃ[ sīvathikaṃ( sī.)] pavicinanto na kiñci gayhūpagaṃ passeyya. "
