822335,153,645,16,54,1,324,32,"So uparimaṃ samāpattiṃ santato manasikaroti, tassa uparimaṃ samāpattiṃ santato manasikaroto catutthajjhāne oḷārikā saññā saṇṭhahati ukkaṇṭhā ca paṭighasaññā, so sabbaso rūpasaññānaṃ samatikkamā paṭighasaññānaṃ atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṃ amanasikārā‘‘ anantaṃ ākāsan’’ ti ākāsānañcāyatanasamāpattiṃ sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
822336,153,645,55,79,1,218,21,"Abhiññābhinīhāro rūpasaññā vokāro nānattasaññā samatikkamati paṭighasaññā cassa abbhatthaṃ gacchati, evaṃ samādhi tassa samāhitassa obhāso antaradhāyati dassanañca rūpānaṃ, so samādhi chaḷaṅgasamannāgato paccavekkhitabbo . "
822337,153,645,80,137,1,364,43,"Anabhijjhāsahagataṃ me mānasaṃ sabbaloke, abyāpannaṃ me cittaṃ sabbasattesu, āraddhaṃ me vīriyaṃ paggahitaṃ, passaddho me kāyo asāraddho, samāhitaṃ me cittaṃ avikkhittaṃ, upaṭṭhitā me sati asammuṭṭhā[ appammuṭṭhā( sī.)], tattha yañca anabhijjhāsahagataṃ mānasaṃ sabbaloke yañca abyāpannaṃ cittaṃ sabbasattesu yañca āraddhaṃ vīriyaṃ paggahitaṃ yañca samāhitaṃ cittaṃ avikkhittaṃ, ayaṃ samatho. "
822338,153,645,138,145,1,50,6,"Yo passaddho kāyo asāraddho, ayaṃ samādhiparikkhāro. "
822339,153,645,146,152,1,43,6,Yā upaṭṭhitā sati asammuṭṭhā ayaṃ vipassanā. 
822340,153,646,2,10,1,33,4,54. So samādhi pañcavidhena veditabbo. 
822341,153,646,11,106,1,527,57,"Ayaṃ samādhi‘‘ paccuppannasukho’’ ti itissa paccattameva ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavati, ayaṃ samādhi‘‘ āyatiṃ sukhavipāko’’ ti itissa paccattameva ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavati, ayaṃ samādhi‘‘ ariyo nirāmiso’’ ti itissa paccattameva ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavati, ayaṃ samādhi‘‘ akāpurisasevito’’ ti itissa paccattameva ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavati, ayaṃ samādhi‘‘ santo ceva paṇīto ca paṭippassaddhiladdho ca ekodibhāvādhigato ca na sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato[ sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritavato( sī.), sasaṅkhāraniggayhavārivāvaṭo( ka.)] cā’’ ti itissa paccattameva ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavati. "
822342,153,646,107,125,1,116,14,Taṃ kho panimaṃ samādhiṃ‘‘ sato samāpajjāmi sato vuṭṭhahāmī’’ ti itissa paccattameva ñāṇadassanaṃ paccupaṭṭhitaṃ bhavati. 
822343,153,646,126,138,1,83,12,Tattha yo ca samādhi paccuppannasukho yo ca samādhi āyatiṃ sukhavipāko ayaṃ samatho. 
822344,153,646,139,176,1,254,33,"Yo ca samādhi ariyo nirāmiso, yo ca samādhi akāpurisasevito, yo ca samādhi santo ceva paṇīto paṭippassaddhiladdho ca ekodibhāvādhigato ca na sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato ca yañcāhaṃ taṃ kho panimaṃ samādhiṃ sato samāpajjāmi sato vuṭṭhahāmīti, ayaṃ vipassanā. "
822345,153,647,2,11,1,113,9,So samādhi pañcavidhena veditabbo pītipharaṇatā sukhapharaṇatā cetopharaṇatā ālokapharaṇatā paccavekkhaṇānimittaṃ. 
822346,153,647,12,25,1,74,12,"Tattha yo ca pītipharaṇo yo ca sukhapharaṇo yo ca cetopharaṇo, ayaṃ samatho. "
822347,153,647,26,31,1,46,5,Yo ca ālokapharaṇo yañca paccavekkhaṇānimittaṃ. 
822348,153,647,32,34,1,14,2,Ayaṃ vipassanā. 
822349,153,648,2,19,1,148,12,55. Dasa kasiṇāyatanāni pathavīkasiṇaṃ āpokasiṇaṃ tejokasiṇaṃ vāyokasiṇaṃ nīlakasiṇaṃ pītakasiṇaṃ lohitakasiṇaṃ odātakasiṇaṃ ākāsakasiṇaṃ viññāṇakasiṇaṃ. 
