822422,153,669,69,88,1,99,13,‘‘ Sabbe sattā marissanti… pe… nirayaṃ pāpakammantā’’ ti ime tayo vaṭṭā dukkhavaṭṭo kammavaṭṭo kilesavaṭṭo.
822423,153,669,89,103,1,72,9,"‘‘ Apare ca maggaṃ bhāvetvā, parinibbantināsavā’’ ti tiṇṇaṃ vaṭṭānaṃ vivaṭṭanā."
822424,153,669,104,141,1,148,20,"‘‘ Sabbe sattā marissanti… pe… nirayaṃ pāpakammantā’’ ti ādīnavo,‘‘ puññakammā ca suggatin’’ ti assādo,‘‘ apare ca maggaṃ bhāvetvā, parinibbantināsavā’’ ti nissaraṇaṃ."
