822751,153,786,2,31,1,192,17,"Manosañcetanāhāro ‘‘ anattani attā’’ ti vipallāso, attavādupādānaṃ, avijjāyogo, idaṃsaccābhinivesakāyagantho, avijjāsavo, avijjogho, mohasallo, saṅkhārūpagā viññāṇaṭṭhiti, mohā agatigamananti catutthī disā. "
822752,153,787,2,44,1,228,28,"Tattha yo ca kabaḷīkāro āhāro yo ca‘‘ asubhe subhan’’ ti vipallāso, kāmupādānaṃ, kāmayogo, abhijjhākāyagantho, kāmāsavo , kāmogho, rāgasallo, rūpūpagā viññāṇaṭṭhiti chandā agatigamananti, imesaṃ dasannaṃ suttānaṃ eko attho, byañjanameva nānaṃ. "
