822759,153,791,2,53,1,286,37,"Tattha yo ca kabaḷīkāro āhāro yo ca phasso āhāro, ime appaṇihitena vimokkhamukhena pariññaṃ gacchanti, viññāṇāhāro suññatāya, manosañcetanāhāro animittena, tattha yo ca‘‘ asubhe subhan’’ ti vipallāso, yo ca‘‘ dukkhe sukhan’’ ti vipallāso, ime appaṇihitena vimokkhamukhena pahānaṃ abbhatthaṃ gacchanti."
822760,153,791,54,73,1,74,10,"‘‘ Anicce niccan’’ ti vipallāso suññatāya,‘‘ anattani attā’’ ti vipallāso animittena. "
822761,153,791,74,81,1,82,7,Tattha kāmupādānañca bhavupādānañca appaṇihitena vimokkhamukhena pahānaṃ gacchanti. 
