824880,155,263,119,165,1,310,39,"Sace pana sīle patiṭṭhito aparāmaṭṭhassa hi sīlavataṃ hoti, tassa taṃ sīlavato yoniso gahitaṃ avippaṭisāraṃ janeti yāva vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ, tañca tassa diṭṭheva dhamme kālaṅkatassa vā tamhiyeva vā pana aparāpariyāyena vā, aññesu khandhesu evaṃ sutaṃ‘‘ sucaritaṃ vāsanāya saṃvattatī’’ ti vāsanābhāgiyaṃ suttaṃ vuccati. "
