826404,155,784,23,26,1,17,3,Tassā ko nissando? 
826405,155,784,27,49,1,165,20,"Dukkhasaññāya bhāvitāya bahulīkatāya ālasse saṃpamāde vimhaye ca cittaṃ nānusandhati na sandhati na saṇṭhahati, upekkhā vā paṭikkūlatā vā saṇṭhahati, ayamassā nissando. "
826406,155,785,2,5,1,25,3,Tattha katamā anattasaññā?
826407,155,785,6,22,1,82,11,"‘‘ Sabbesu dhammesu anattā’’ ti yā saññā sañjānanā vavatthapanā uggāho, ayaṃ anattasaññā. "
826408,155,785,23,48,1,174,21,"Tassā ko nissando, anattasaññāya bhāvitāya bahulīkatāya ahaṅkāro cittaṃ nānusandhati na sandhati, mamaṅkāro na saṇṭhahati, upekkhā vā paṭikkūlatā vā saṇṭhahati, ayamassā nissando. "
