826668,155,837,2,3,1,16,1,Pakiṇṇakaniddeso . 
826669,155,838,2,37,1,119,18,"74. Yāni cattāri jhānāni, tesaṃ jhānānaṃ imāni aṅgāni, tesaṃ aṅgānaṃ samūho[ sammoho( pī. ka.)] assa aṅgā, ayaṃ jhānabhūmi ko visesoti assa viseso. "
826670,155,838,38,53,1,94,13,"Ime sambhārā tehi ayaṃ samudāgamo, tassa samudāgamassa ayaṃ upanisā, tāya upanisāya ayaṃ bhāvanā. "
