827454,155,945,87,89,1,11,2,Kiṃ kāraṇaṃ? 
827455,155,945,90,119,1,182,24,"Dosanīye panassanti na dussati, aduṭṭhaṃ taṃ na kosissanti, tena kuppanīye na kuppati, yassevaṃ bhāvitaṃ cittaṃ kuto taṃ dukkhaniddeso ca kuto evarūpassa dukkhaṃ āgamissatīti niddiṭṭhaṃ. "
827456,155,946,2,15,1,105,13,Parivattanāti kuto taṃ dukkhamessatīti yaṃ cetasikaṃ sukhaṃ anupādisesā ayaṃ natthi sopādisesā ayaṃ atthi. 
827457,155,946,16,37,1,167,21,Puna evamāhaṃsu taṃ khaṇaṃ taṃ muhuttaṃ ubhayameva avedayitaṃ sopādisesaṃ yañca anupādisesaṃ yañca taṃ khaṇaṃ taṃ muhuttaṃ anupādisesaṃ yañca sopādisesaṃ ca avedayitaṃ. 
827458,155,946,38,43,1,58,5,Sukhamāpannassa anāvattikanti ayamettha viseso parivattanā. 
827459,155,947,2,6,1,22,3,Tattha katamo vevacano? 
827460,155,947,7,16,1,84,9,Yassevaṃ bhāvitaṃ cittaṃ vā bhāvitaṃ subhāvitaṃ anuṭṭhitaṃ vatthukataṃ susamāraddhaṃ. 
827461,155,947,17,22,1,51,5,Cittanti mano viññāṇaṃ manindriyaṃ manoviññāṇadhātu. 
827462,155,948,2,6,1,22,3,Tattha katamā paññatti? 
827463,155,948,7,12,1,49,5,Cittaṃ mano saṅkhārā vūpasamapaññattiyā paññattaṃ. 
827464,155,948,13,16,1,34,3,Samādhi asekkhapaññattiyā paññatto. 
827465,155,948,17,20,1,36,3,Dukkhaṃ ucchinnapaññattiyā paññattaṃ. 
827466,155,949,2,5,1,21,3,Tattha katamo otaraṇo? 
827467,155,949,6,26,1,154,17,"Citte niddiṭṭhe pañcakkhandhā niddiṭṭhā honti, ayaṃ khandhesu otaraṇo, manoviññāṇadhātuyā niddiṭṭhāya aṭṭhārasa dhātuyo niddiṭṭhā honti, ayaṃ dhātūsu otaraṇo. "
827468,155,949,27,33,1,56,6,Manāyatane niddiṭṭhe sabbāni āyatanāni niddiṭṭhāni honti. 
827469,155,949,34,38,1,42,4,Tattha manāyatanaṃ nāmarūpassa padaṭṭhānaṃ. 
827470,155,949,39,41,1,27,2,Nāmarūpapaccayā saḷāyatanaṃ. 
827471,155,949,42,44,1,22,2,Tathā paṭiccasamuppāde. 
827472,155,949,45,47,1,12,2,Ayaṃ otaraṇo. 
827473,155,949,48,53,1,40,5,Tattha katamo sodhano suddhoyeva ārambho. 
827474,155,950,2,5,1,24,3,Tattha katamo adhiṭṭhāno? 
827475,155,950,6,14,1,74,8,Chaḷindriyaṃ bhāvanā ekattāyaṃ paññatti chaṭṭhitena kāyo ekattāya paññatto. 
827476,155,951,2,5,1,24,3,Tattha katamo parikkhāro? 
827477,155,951,6,33,1,214,25,"Cittassa pubbahetu samuppādāya manasikāro ca tappoṇatā ca yaṃ asamāhitabhūmiyaṃ ca visesadhammānaṃ abhāvitattā cittasatataṃ gacchati, sace samādhino sukhaṃ hetu avippaṭisāro paccayo, ayaṃ hetu ayaṃ paccayo parikkhāro. "
827478,155,952,2,6,1,24,3,Tattha katamā samāropanā? 
827479,155,952,7,12,1,48,5,Yassevaṃ bhāvitanti tassa dhammā samāropayitabbā. 
827480,155,952,13,34,1,185,21,Kāyo sīlaṃ paññā bhāvitacittanti anabhirataṃ anapaṇataṃ anekaṃ anutaṃ anāpajjāsattaṃ ayaṃ samaññāyatanā na tassa sekkhassa sammāsamādhi sabbe asekkhā dasa arahantadhammā niddiṭṭhā honti. 
827481,155,952,35,37,1,24,2,Asekkhabhāgiyāni suttāni. 
827482,155,953,2,53,1,307,32,"96. Yassa nūna, bhante, kāyagatāsati abhāvitā, ayaṃ so aññataraṃ sabrahmacāriṃ[ sabrahmacārīnaṃ( ka.)] āsajja samāpajja appaṭinisajja janapadacārikaṃ pakkameyya, so āyasmā imasmiṃ vippaṭijānāti dve pajāni paṭijānāti cittabhāvanāyañca diṭṭhiyā pahānaṃ, kāyabhāvanāyañca diṭṭhippahānaṃ, kāyabhāvanāyañca taṇhāpahānaṃ, yaṃ paṭhamaṃ upamaṃ karoti. "
827483,155,953,54,76,1,166,20,"Asucināpi sucināpi pathavī neva aṭṭiyati na jigucchati na pītipāmojjaṃ paṭilabhati, evameva hi pathavīsamena so cetasā anvayena appakena averena abyāpajjena viharāmīti. "
827484,155,953,77,90,1,121,11,"Iti so āyasmā kiṃ paṭijānāti, kāyabhāvanāya sukhindriyapahānaṃ paṭijānāti, cittabhāvanāya somanassindriyapahānaṃ paṭijānāti. "
827485,155,953,91,96,1,61,5,Kāyikā vedanā rāgānusayamanugatānaṃ sukhindriyaṃ paṭikkhipati. 
827486,155,953,97,109,1,102,12,Na hi vedanākkhandhaṃ yā cetasikā sukhavedanā tattha ayaṃ paṭilābhapaccayā uppajjati sukhaṃ somanassaṃ. 
827487,155,953,110,117,1,49,6,"Sotaṃ paṭikkhipati, na hi manosamphassajaṃ vedanaṃ. "
827488,155,953,118,124,1,71,6,Tattha catūsu mahābhūtesu rūpakkhandhassa anusayapaṭighapahānaṃ bhaṇati. 
827489,155,953,125,129,1,34,4,Kāme rūpañca tañca asekkhabhūmiyaṃ. 
827490,155,953,130,133,1,45,3,Kāye kāyānupassanā diṭṭhadhammasukhavihārañca. 
827491,155,953,134,168,1,235,31,"Balena ca ussāhena ca sabbaṃ manasi katattānaṃ pahānaṃ medaṃ katālikāya ca purisena ca maṇḍanakajātikena ca, etehi imassa mātāpitusambhūtaṃ paccavekkhaṇaṃ, so kāyena ca kāyānupassanāya ca cittena ca cittānupassanāya ca dve dhamme dhāreti. "
827492,155,953,169,180,1,111,11,Kāyakilesavatthuṃ cittena ca cittasannissaye cittena subhāvitena sattannaṃ ca samāpattīnaṃ viharituṃ paṭijānāti. 
827493,155,954,2,53,1,370,34,"Gahapatiputtopamatāya ca yathā gahapatiputtassa nānāraṅgānaṃ vatthakaraṇḍako puṇṇo bhaveyya, so yaṃ yadeva vatthayugaṃ pubbaṇhasamaye ākaṅkhati, pubbaṇhasamaye nibbāpeti, evaṃ majjhanhikasamaye, sāyanhasamaye, evameva so āyasmā cittassa subhāvitattā yathārūpena vihārena ākaṅkhati pubbaṇhasamayaṃ viharituṃ, tathārūpena[ yathārūpena( pī. ka.)] pubbaṇhasamayaṃ viharati, majjhanhikasamaye, sāyanhasamaye. "
827494,155,954,54,65,1,87,11,Tena vesa āyasmatā upamāya me āsitāya pathavī vā anuttarā indriyabhāvanā bhāvitacittena. 
827495,155,954,66,89,1,197,21,"Tena so āyasmā idaṃ aṭṭhavidhaṃ bhāvanaṃ paṭijānāti catūsu mahābhūtesu, kāyabhāvanaṃ upakacaṇḍālaṃ purisametakaṃ bhavatalākāsu cittabhāvanaṃ, imāhi bhāvanāhi tāya bhāvanāya ca samathā pāripūrimantehi. "
827496,155,954,90,93,1,33,3,Imehi catūhi paññāpāripūrimantehi. 
827497,155,955,2,13,1,65,6,97. Kathaṃ upakacaṇḍālaṃ paṭikūlesu dhammesu appaṭikūlasaññī viharati? 
827498,155,955,14,40,1,218,24,"Kāyo pakatiyā appaṭikūlaṃ kāye uddhumātakasaññā saṃkhittena nava saññā ime paṭikūlā dhammā ceso āyasmā paṭikūlato ajigucchito kāyagatāsatiyā bhāvanānuyogamanuyutto viharati, na hi tassa jigucchappahāya cittaṃ paṭikūlati. "
827499,155,956,2,8,1,53,5,Kathaṃ appaṭikūlesu dhammesu paṭikūlasaññī viharatīti? 
827500,155,956,9,17,1,65,8,Kāyo sabbalokassa appaṭikūlo taṃ so āyasmā asubhasaññāya viharati. 
827501,155,956,18,23,1,49,5,Evaṃ appaṭikūlesu dhammesu paṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
827502,155,957,2,38,1,302,34,"Kathaṃ paṭikūlesu ca appaṭikūlesu ca appaṭikūlasaññī viharatīti api sabboyaṃ lokassa yamidaṃ muṇḍo pattapāṇī kulesu piṇḍāya vicarati, tena ca so āyasmā suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇena appaṭikūlasaññī cittena ca kāyena nibbidāsahagatena appaṭikūlasaññī, evaṃ paṭikūlesu appaṭikūlesu ca dhammesu appaṭikūlasaññī viharati. "
827503,155,958,2,8,1,54,6,Kathaṃ paṭikūlesu ca dhammesu appaṭikūlasaññī viharati? 
827504,155,958,9,23,1,128,14,Paṭikūlesu ca dhammesu subhasaññino itthirūpe paṭikūlesu ca jigucchino vinīlakavipubbake tattha so āyasmā paṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
827505,155,959,2,13,1,94,11,Kathaṃ paṭikūlesu dhammesu tadubhayaṃ abhinivajjayitvā upekkhako viharati sato ca sampajāno ca? 
827506,155,959,14,38,1,165,18,Appaṭikūlesu ca dhammesu subhasaññino itthirūpe paṭikūlesu ca jigucchino vinīlakavipubbake tadubhayaṃ abhinivajjayitvā‘ netaṃ mama’‘ nesohamasmi’‘ neso me’ attāti viharati. 
827507,155,959,39,47,1,66,7,Evaṃ tadubhayaṃ abhinivajjayitvā upekkhako viharati sato sampajāno. 
827508,155,960,2,4,1,14,2,Aparo pariyāyo. 
827509,155,960,5,9,1,62,4,Tedhātuko lokasannivāso sabbabālaputhujjanānaṃ appaṭikūlasaññā. 
827510,155,960,10,16,1,51,6,Tattha ca āyasmā sāriputto appaṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
827511,155,960,17,22,1,49,5,Evaṃ appaṭikūlesu dhammesu paṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
