827513,155,961,8,14,1,55,6,Paṭikūlasaññino sabbasekkhā idha kā tedhātuke sabbaloke. 
827514,155,961,15,23,1,74,7,Tattha katamo bhūmippatto samādhiphale sacchikato appaṭikūlasaññī viharati ? 
827515,155,961,24,26,1,11,2,Kiṃ kāraṇaṃ? 
827516,155,961,27,36,1,62,9,Na hi taṃ atthi yassa lokassa pahānāya paṭikūlasaññī uppādeyya. 
827517,155,962,2,10,1,68,8,Kathaṃ paṭikūlesu ca appaṭikūlesu ca dhammesu paṭikūlasaññī viharati? 
827518,155,962,11,21,1,114,10,Tedhātuke lokasannivāse yāva kāmalokabhūmatā hi rāgānaṃ vītarāgānaṃ paṭikūlasamatā rūpārūpadhātuṃ appaṭikūlasamatā. 
827519,155,962,22,28,1,49,6,Tattha ca āyasmā sāriputto paṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
