827522,155,963,12,27,1,133,15,Yaṃ kiñci parato duruttānaṃ durāgatānaṃ vacanapathānaṃ taṃ vacanaṃ appaṭikūlaṃ yāvatā vācaso appatirūpā tathā janassa appaṭikūlasaññā. 
827523,155,963,28,44,1,138,15,"Tattha āyasmā sāriputto abhiññāya sacchikato appaṭikūlasaññī viharati, evaṃ paṭikūlesu ca appaṭikūlesu ca dhammesu appaṭikūlasaññī viharati. "
827524,155,964,2,21,1,113,14,98. Kathaṃ paṭikūlesu ca appaṭikūlesu ca dhammesu tadubhayaṃ abhinivajjayitvā upekkhako ca viharati sato ca sampajāno? 
827525,155,964,22,32,1,66,9,"Yañca nesaṃ samanupassati ye dhammā duccaritā, te dhammā appaṭikūlā. "
827526,155,964,33,45,1,87,11,"Tattha āyasmā sāriputto iti paṭisañcikkhati ye dhammā duccaritā, te dhammā aniṭṭhavipākā. "
827527,155,964,46,52,1,33,5,"Ye dhammā sucaritā, te ācayagāmino. "
827528,155,964,53,65,1,117,12,So ca sucaritaṃ ācayagāminiṃ karitvā duccaritaṃ aniṭṭhavipākaṃ karitvā tadubhayaṃ abhinivajjayitvā upekkhako viharati. 
827529,155,965,2,10,1,66,8,Atha paṭikūlesu ca dhammesu appaṭikūlesu ca paṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
827530,155,965,11,15,1,32,4,Taṇhā paṭikūladhammā kiṃ kāraṇaṃ? 
827531,155,965,16,31,1,102,13,"Taṇhāvasena hi sattā dvīhi dhammehi sattā, kabaḷīkāre āhāre rasataṇhāya sattā, phasse sukhasaññāya sattā. "
827532,155,965,32,44,1,95,11,"Tatthāyasmā sāriputto kabaḷīkāre ca āhāre paṭikūlasaññī viharati, phasse ca dukkhasaññī viharati. "
827533,155,965,45,52,1,57,7,Evaṃ paṭikūlesu ca appaṭikūlesu ca paṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
827534,155,966,2,11,1,79,9,Kathaṃ paṭikūlesu ca dhammesu appaṭikūlesu ca dhammesu appaṭikūlasaññī viharati? 
827535,155,966,12,20,1,84,8,Taṇhākkhayaṃ anuttaraṃ nibbānaṃ tathā bālaputhujjanānaṃ paṭikūlasaññā pahatasaññā ca. 
827536,155,966,21,36,1,135,14,Tatthāyasmato sāriputtassa appaṭikūlasaññā abyāpādasaññā ca sāmaṃ paññāya passitvā evaṃ paṭikūlesu ca dhammesu appaṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
827537,155,967,2,10,1,70,8,Kathaṃ paṭikūlesu ca appaṭikūlesu ca dhammesu appaṭikūlasaññī viharati? 
827538,155,967,11,21,1,72,9,Tatiye ca nibbāne paṭikūlasaññino yasena ca kittini ca appaṭikūlasaññino. 
827539,155,967,22,37,1,179,15,Tatthāyasmā sāriputto assādañca ādīnavañca nissaraṇañca yathābhūtaṃ sammāpaññāya paṭijānanto paṭikūlañca appaṭikūlañca dhammaṃ tadubhayaṃ abhinivajjayitvā appaṭikūlasaññī viharati. 
827540,155,968,2,11,1,85,8,Kathaṃ paṭikūlaṃ appaṭikūlañca dhammaṃ tadubhayaṃ abhinivajjayitvā upekkhako viharati? 
827541,155,968,12,36,1,181,22,"Sato ca sampajāno ca, yañca samanupassati anunayo appaṭikūlo dhammo paṭigho ca paṭikūlo dhammo, tatthāyasmā sāriputto anunayassa paṭighappahīnattā upekkhako viharati sato sampajāno ca. "
827542,155,968,37,43,1,62,6,Yañcassa samanupassati ayaṃ pañcavidhā anuttarā indriyabhāvanā. 
827543,155,968,44,46,1,17,2,Ayaṃ suttaniddeso. 
