827727,155,1008,82,90,1,39,6,"Kathaṃ pavatti hoti, kathaṃ nivatti hoti? "
827728,155,1008,91,98,1,37,6,"Kathaṃ bandho hoti, kathaṃ mokkho hoti? "
827729,155,1008,99,106,1,54,6,"Kathaṃ sakkāyasamudayo hoti, kathaṃ sakkāyanirodho hoti? "
827730,155,1008,107,117,1,72,10,So ettha desitaṃ yathā upaṭṭhitaṃ tathā sampaṭipajjanto so evaṃ pajānāti. 
827731,155,1008,118,125,1,36,6,"Ime dhammā kusalā, ime dhammā akusalā. "
827732,155,1008,126,140,1,89,11,"Evaṃ… pe… yāva kathaṃ sakkāyasamudayo hoti, kathaṃ sakkāyanirodho hotīti vitthārena kātabbaṃ. "
827733,155,1008,141,151,1,72,10,So te dhamme adhipāṭikaṅkhāti evaṃ lakkhaṇaṃ ñāṇaṃ vijjā ālokaṃ vaḍḍheti. 
827734,155,1008,152,163,1,79,10,"So puggalo tapparamo bhavati tapparāyano, ayaṃ vuccate puggalo joti jotiparāyano. "
827735,155,1009,2,7,1,39,5,Tattha katamo puggalo tamo tamaparāyano? 
827736,155,1009,8,12,1,26,4,Yo akusalaṃ dhammaṃ dīpeti. 
827737,155,1009,13,23,1,75,9,"Taṃ bhāvanāya hīnāsu gatīsu upapattiṃ dasseti, tapparamo bhavati tapparāyano. "
