827740,155,1010,8,14,1,45,6,So tamena akusalassa kammassa vipākaṃ dasseti. 
827741,155,1010,15,27,1,89,11,"Tameti yaṃ cakkhu kalyāṇamittassa yena akusale dhamme pajahati, kusale dhamme abhivaḍḍhati. "
827742,155,1011,2,16,1,87,12,"Tattha yo ca paṇītāsu gatīsu upapattiṃ dasseti, tapparamo tena vuccate tamo jotiparāyano. "
827743,155,1012,2,7,1,35,5,Tattha yo puggalo joti tamaparāyano? 
