828399,155,1169,2,6,1,29,4,Tattha katamo tipukkhalo nayo? 
828400,155,1169,7,28,1,158,20,"Ye ca dukkhāya paṭipadāya dandhābhiññāya khippābhiññāya ca niyyanti dve puggalā, ye ca sukhāya paṭipadāya dandhābhiññāya khippābhiññāya ca niyyanti dve puggalā. "
828401,155,1170,2,19,1,136,16,"Imesaṃ catunnaṃ puggalānaṃ yo puggalo sukhāya paṭipadāya dandhābhiññāya niyyāti, yo ca puggalo dukkhāya paṭipadāya khippābhiññāya niyyāti. "
828402,155,1170,20,24,1,24,4,Ime dve puggalā bhavanti. 
828403,155,1170,25,35,1,69,8,"Tattha yo sukhāya paṭipadāya khippābhiññāya niyyāti , ayaṃ ugghaṭitaññū. "
828404,155,1170,36,43,1,47,6,"Yo pacchimo puggalo sādhāraṇo, ayaṃ vipañcitaññū. "
828405,155,1170,44,53,1,64,8,"Yo puggalo dandhābhiññāya dukkhāya paṭipadāya niyyāti, ayaṃ neyyo. "
828406,155,1170,54,72,1,163,15,"Ime cattāro bhavitvā tīṇi honti, tattha ugghaṭitaññussa samathapubbaṅgamā vipassanā, neyyassa vipassanāpubbaṅgamo samatho, vipañcitaññussa samathavipassanā yuganaddhā. "
