828409,155,1171,11,17,1,48,6,Iti imesaṃ puggalānaṃ catūhi paṭipadāhi niyyānaṃ. 
828410,155,1172,2,25,1,163,21,"Tattha ayaṃ saṃkileso, tīṇi akusalamūlāni tayo phassā tisso vedanā tayo upavicārā tayo saṃkilesā tayo vitakkā tayo pariḷāhā tīṇi saṅkhatalakkhaṇāni tisso dukkhatāti. "
828411,155,1173,2,12,1,75,8,"Tīṇi akusalamūlānīti lobho akusalamūlaṃ, doso akusalamūlaṃ, moho akusalamūlaṃ. "
