828414,155,1173,33,38,1,68,5,Tayo upavicārāti somanassopavicāro domanassopavicāro upekkhopavicāro. 
828415,155,1173,39,44,1,31,5,Tayo saṃkilesāti rāgo doso moho. 
828416,155,1173,45,50,1,56,5,Tayo vitakkāti kāmavitakko byāpādavitakko vihiṃsāvitakko. 
828417,155,1173,51,57,1,36,5,Tayo pariḷāhāti rāgajo dosajo mohajo. 
828418,155,1173,58,63,1,43,5,Tīṇi saṅkhatalakkhaṇānīti uppādo ṭhiti vayo. 
828419,155,1173,64,69,1,67,5,Tisso dukkhatāti dukkhadukkhatā vipariṇāmadukkhatā saṅkhatadukkhatā. 
828420,155,1174,2,7,1,42,5,Tattha lobho akusalamūlaṃ kuto samuṭṭhitaṃ? 
828421,155,1174,8,13,1,57,5,Tividhaṃ ārammaṇaṃ manāpikaṃ amanāpikaṃ upekkhāṭhāniyañca. 
828422,155,1174,14,20,1,60,6,Tattha manāpikena ārammaṇena lobho akusalamūlaṃ samuṭṭhahati. 
828423,155,1174,21,66,1,392,38,"Iti manāpikā ārammaṇā sukhavedanīyo phasso, sukhavedanīyaṃ phassaṃ paṭicca uppajjate sukhavedanā, sukhavedanaṃ paṭicca uppajjate somanassūpavicāro, somanassūpavicāraṃ paṭicca uppajjate rāgo, rāgaṃ paṭicca uppajjate kāmavitakko, kāmavitakkaṃ paṭicca uppajjate rāgajo pariḷāho rāgajaṃ pariḷāhaṃ paṭicca uppajjate uppādo saṅkhatalakkhaṇo, uppādaṃ saṅkhatalakkhaṇaṃ paṭicca uppajjate vipariṇāmadukkhatā. "
828424,155,1175,2,7,1,34,4,Doso akusalamūlaṃ kuto samuṭṭhitaṃ? 
828425,155,1175,8,13,1,52,5,Amanāpikena ārammaṇena doso akusalamūlaṃ samuṭṭhitaṃ. 
828426,155,1175,14,62,1,434,41,"Iti amanāpikā ārammaṇā dukkhavedanīyo phasso, dukkhavedanīyaṃ phassaṃ paṭicca uppajjate dukkhavedanā, dukkhavedanaṃ paṭicca uppajjate domanassūpavicāro, domanassūpavicāraṃ paṭicca uppajjate doso, dosaṃ paṭicca uppajjate byāpādavitakko, byāpādavitakkaṃ paṭicca uppajjate dosajo pariḷāho, dosajaṃ pariḷāhaṃ paṭicca uppajjate ṭhitassa aññathattaṃ saṅkhatalakkhaṇaṃ, ṭhitassa aññathattaṃ saṅkhatalakkhaṇaṃ paṭicca uppajjate dukkhadukkhatā vedanā. "
828427,155,1176,2,6,1,34,4,Moho akusalamūlaṃ kuto samuṭṭhitaṃ? 
828428,155,1176,7,12,1,57,5,Upekkhāṭhāniyena ārammaṇena moho akusalamūlaṃ samuṭṭhitaṃ. 
828429,155,1176,13,71,1,508,49,"Iti upekkhāṭhāniyā ārammaṇā adukkhamasukhavedanīyo phasso, adukkhamasukhavedanīyaṃ phassaṃ paṭicca uppajjate adukkhamasukhā vedanā, adukkhamasukhavedanaṃ paṭicca uppajjate upekkhūpavicāro, upekkhūpavicāraṃ paṭicca uppajjate moho, mohaṃ paṭicca uppajjate vihiṃsāvitakko, vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ paṭicca uppajjate mohajo pariḷāho, mohajaṃ pariḷāhaṃ paṭicca uppajjate vayo saṅkhatalakkhaṇaṃ, vayaṃ saṅkhatalakkhaṇaṃ paṭicca uppajjate saṅkhatadukkhatā, iti ayaṃ tiṇṇaṃ kilesānaṃ niddeso, ayaṃ vuccate kusalapakkhe tipukkhalo nayo. "
828430,155,1177,2,27,1,161,21,"Iti tīṇi akusalamūlāni na catutthāni na pañcamāni, tayo phassāti tisso vedanā yāva saṅkhatadukkhatāti, yo koci akusalapakkho, sabbo so tīsu akusalamūlesu samosarati. "
828431,155,1178,2,6,1,26,3,Tattha katamo kusalapakkho? 
828432,155,1178,7,18,1,78,10,"Tīṇi kusalamūlāni, tisso paññā sutamayī paññā cintāmayī paññā bhāvanāmayī paññā. "
