828466,155,1189,44,51,1,53,7,Imesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ nayānaṃ paṭhamo nayo sīhavikkīḷito nāma. 
828467,155,1189,52,68,1,113,15,"Aṭṭha padāni cattāri ca kusalāni cattāri ca akusalāni imāni aṭṭha padāni mūlapadāni, atthanayena dutiyo tipukkhalo. "
828468,155,1189,69,92,1,159,22,"So chahi dhammehi neti kusalamūlāni ca neti akusalamūlāni ca, iti imāni cha padāni purimakāni ca aṭṭha mūlapadāni imāni cuddasa padāni aṭṭhārasannaṃ mūlapadānaṃ. "
828469,155,1189,93,104,1,62,9,"Tattha yo pacchimako nayo nandiyāvaṭṭo, so catūhi dhammehi neti. "
828470,155,1189,105,123,1,120,17,"Avijjāya ca taṇhāya ca samathena ca vipassanāya ca, ime cattāro dhammā imāni aṭṭhārasa mūlapadāni tīsu nayesu niddiṭṭhāni. "
